text: 2023 AFC Asian Cup was held in Qatar from 12 January to 10 February. Qatar Was Champions of The 2023 AFC Asian Cup ==Teams== ===Qualified teams=== 24 teams qualified, with Japan being the first team to qualify for the main stage. ;CAFA (4) * * * * ;EFF (4) * * * * ;AFF (5) * * * * * ;Clear (1) * ;WAF (10) * * (host) * * * * * * * * == Venues == City Stadium Capacity Al Khor Al Bayt Stadium 68,895 Lusail Lusail Stadium 88,966 Al Rayyan Ahmad bin Ali Stadium 45,032 Education City Stadium 44,667 Jassim bin Hamad Stadium 15,000 Khalifa International Stadium 45,857 Doha Abdullah bin Khalifa Stadium 10,000 Al Thumama Stadium 44,400 Al Wakrah Al Janoub Stadium 44,325 == Squads == Each team participating in this tournament must register a squad consisting of a minimum of 18 players and a maximum of 23 players including three goalkeepers.
